
If you want to see statistics in Grafana, you need to install Prometheus and Grafana.

--> I have installed Grafana and Prometheus on my local machine.

--> Go to C folder --> tools --> prometheus --> run the app
--> Then go to web and hit http://localhost:9090/targets to see the targets that are being monitored by Prometheus. You should see your application listed there.
--> Now, open Grafana by going to http://localhost:3000/ and log in with the default credentials (admin/admin).
--> Once logged in, click on "Add your first data source" and select "Prometheus" from the list of available data sources.
